{"tid":2432674,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"男子瞞騙老婆入手 PS5   找 Sony 員工假扮寬頻公司職員安裝","createTime":"2021-03-04T13:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T03:55:38.000Z","uid":58335,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2add4036ea6f3af5de4fd3da6f96b57738906d4f","tid":2432674,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:05:54.000Z","msg":"當 Sony 發表 PS5 時，不少被老婆嚴密監控的男士都笑說，藉口改善家中上網質素，將 PS5 扮成 Wi-Fi 路由器去魚目混珠。想不到這個想法竟然有男士付諸行動，有一名越南男士購買了 PS5 後，為了不讓老婆知道，於是要求 Sony 的員工協助隱瞞。<br />\n<br />\n該名男士請 Sony 的員工穿著當地寬頻公司的制服，藉詞上門安裝 5G Wi-Fi 路由器；做戲做全套，男子甚至準備了寬頻公司的售後服務熱線貼紙，貼在 PS5 的機身以免老婆懷疑。到底該名男子能夠瞞騙老婆多久，最後有什麼下場，外國媒體未有跟進報導，但他將整個過程拍攝和上載到社交平台，就引來了網民瘋傳，相信他的老婆已經得悉事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為了「偷運」PS5 入屋，男士們無所不用其極，之前網傳有台灣玩家將 PS5 說成是空氣淨化機，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">後來被老婆拆穿後，被逼在市場嚴重缺貨的情況下，以低於市價的方式放售。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n資料來源：gizmochina<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1144/27796/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fnb%2Ftalk%2F1144%2F27796%2F1%2F&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv6VNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=dc1ed775\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1144/27796/1/</a>"},{"pid":"2f33bd863688cd49dbbd8c7d228839db54403e73","tid":2432674,"uid":362827,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:08:10.000Z","msg":"男人老狗做到咁撚垃圾都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，買PS5關佢撚事"},{"pid":"e2502114364f6b5ba931ecbac8ffc6a3234672e4","tid":2432674,"uid":187889,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T13:08:16.000Z","msg":"Plashspeed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fbdfc18d8ec58b3c179fab117280e74dedd0421","tid":2432674,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"